♪Should I leave or stay♪

841
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:57,370
♪I can give up my dignity♪

842
00:38:57,530 --> 00:39:00,570
♪That I care about♪

843
00:39:02,300 --> 00:39:05,820
♪The past and former days♪

844
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:10,090
♪All have gone♪

845
00:39:10,410 --> 00:39:12,990
♪Let it go with the flow♪

846
00:39:12,990 --> 00:39:17,000
♪Memories are close at hand♪

847
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:21,220
♪Behind those smiles with tears♪

848
00:39:21,220 --> 00:39:24,490
♪Is silence♪

849
